{"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib","doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/SourceProtocol"]]},"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/SourceProtocol\/set(readyTime:)"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/glib\/sourceprotocol\/set(readytime:)"]}],"metadata":{"extendedModule":"GLib","roleHeading":"Instance Method","modules":[{"name":"GLib"}],"externalID":"s:4GLib14SourceProtocolPAAE3set9readyTimeys5Int64V_tF","symbolKind":"method","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"set"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"readyTime"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@gint64","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"gint64"},{"text":")","kind":"text"}],"role":"symbol","title":"set(readyTime:)"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets a source to be dispatched when the given monotonic time is"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"reached (or passed).","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"set","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"readyTime","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@gint64","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"gint64"},{"kind":"text","text":")"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If the monotonic time is in the past (as it"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"always will be if ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"readyTime"},{"text":" is ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"0"},{"text":") then the source will be","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"dispatched immediately.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"readyTime"},{"text":" is ","type":"text"},{"code":"-1","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" then the source is never woken up on the basis","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of the passage of time."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Dispatching the source does not reset the ready time.  You should do","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"so yourself, from the source dispatch function.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Note that if you have a pair of sources where the ready time of one","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"suggests that it will be delivered first but the priority for the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"other suggests that it would be delivered first, and the ready time","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"for both sources is reached during the same main context iteration,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"then the order of dispatch is undefined."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"It is a no-op to call this function on a [struct","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/Source"},{"type":"text","text":"] which has"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"already been destroyed with [method"},{"code":"GLib.Source.destroy","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"]."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This API is only intended to be used by implementations of [struct"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/Source"},{"type":"text","text":"]."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Do not call this API on a [struct","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documenta